headline: Nvidia vs. AMD: Which Is the Better AI Chip Stock for 2025?
summary: Nvidia (NASDAQ: NVDA) is by far the leader in the space.  Rival Advanced Micro Devices (NASDAQ: AMD), meanwhile, is trying to take Nvidia on and gain a meaningful share of the data center market.  In 2024, Nvidia's stock has been the clear winner, trading up by about 175% as of this writing.
